<Base title="The System" description="The tabletop rules of play for Saints of Avilund — character generation, mechanics, and Game Master tools. Currently in design.">
  <p class="eyebrow">The System</p>
  <h1>Rules of Play</h1>
  <p class="lede">
    The character system, the mechanics, and the Game Master&rsquo;s tools — currently in design.
  </p>

  <div class="prose" style="margin:0 auto;">
    <p>
      <em>Saints of Avilund</em> is a tabletop role-playing game. The full rules &mdash; character
      creation, progression, magic, combat, and the Game Master&rsquo;s section &mdash; are still being
      designed and tested, and will appear here when they are ready. The Players&rsquo; section and the
      Game Masters&rsquo; section will be split apart once the rules stabilise.
    </p>
    <p>
      In the meantime, the <a href={url('setting/')}>Setting</a> grows steadily, and the
      <a href={url('scriptorium/')}>Designers&rsquo; Notes</a> track what is underway.
    </p>
  </div>
